---
import LayoutSidebar from '../../layouts/LayoutSidebar.astro';

const sidebarMenu = {
    title: "Fasilitas Ruangan",
    items: [
        {"label": "Lantai 1", "href": "/fasilitas/lantai-1"},
        {"label": "Lantai 2", "href": "/fasilitas/lantai-2"},
        {"label": "Lantai 3", "href": "/fasilitas/lantai-3"},
        {"label": "Reservasi Ruangan", "href": "/reservasi"}
    ]
};
---

<LayoutSidebar title="Fasilitas Lantai 1" sidebarMenu={sidebarMenu}>
    
    <div class="mb-8">
        <p class="font-serif text-[15px] text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0 max-w-3xl">Lantai dasar yang dirancang dinamis sebagai zona sirkulasi untuk memudahkan akses seluruh pengunjung.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Fasilitas Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:lock"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Loker</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Tempat penyimpanan tas dan barang bawaan pengunjung. Disediakan secara khusus agar area membaca perpustakaan tetap rapi, nyaman, dan barang bawaan Anda terjamin keamanannya.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:bookmark"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Pengolahan Bahan Pustaka</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Pusat kerja di balik layar, tempat dilakukannya serangkaian proses penting seperti katalogisasi, klasifikasi, pelabelan, hingga penataan koleksi secara fisik sebelum dilayankan kepada publik.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:print"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Fotocopy</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Layanan mandiri untuk kebutuhan fotokopi dan penggandaan dokumen rujukan. Dirancang untuk membantu kelancaran akses referensi akademik para sivitas akademika.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:water"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Mushola</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Fasilitas tempat ibadah yang senantiasa dijaga kebersihan dan kenyamanannya, didedikasikan bagi para pengunjung maupun staf operasional perpustakaan.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:conference-call"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Meeting</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Ruang pertemuan yang difungsikan sebagai pusat koordinasi internal. Sering digunakan untuk rapat rutin, diskusi, dan pembinaan pengembangan layanan perpustakaan.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:reading"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Pojok Baca</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Area dengan suasana yang lebih santai dan rileks. Tempat yang sangat tenang, kondusif, dan nyaman bagi pengunjung untuk membaca buku favoritnya.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:clock"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Tunggu</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Area persinggahan bagi pemustaka yang sedang menunggu giliran pelayanan, atau sekadar beristirahat dengan suasana ruangan yang nyaman dan sejuk.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:manager"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Kepala Perpustakaan</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Pusat manajemen dan administrasi di mana berbagai langkah koordinasi, serta pengambilan keputusan strategis terkait pengembangan layanan perpustakaan dilakukan.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-blue-200">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:like"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Laktasi</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Fasilitas ruang privat yang dirancang untuk memberikan kenyamanan dan keamanan khusus bagi ibu menyusui di lingkungan perpustakaan.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:collaborator-male"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Staf</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Pusat operasional dan tata usaha, di mana para staf perpustakaan menjalankan tugas administrasi harian, manajemen layanan, serta pengelolaan institusi perpustakaan.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-[8px] p-6 border border-[#dadada] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#BBF7D0] transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#F0FDF4] rounded-[8px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#168940] mb-4 border border-[#dadada] group-hover:border-[#BBF7D0]">
                <iconify-icon icon="flat-color-icons:webcam"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#222222] mb-2 m-0 tracking-tight">Ruang Server dan CCTV</h3>
            <p class="font-serif text-sm text-[#444444] leading-relaxed m-0">
                Pusat kontrol infrastruktur keamanan dan jaringan perpustakaan. Berfungsi sebagai area pengawasan area membaca melalui CCTV serta pangkalan data server lokal.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

</LayoutSidebar>
